{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/Flex/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h1>Flex</h1>\n<p>레이아웃을 정의할 때 특히, 수평정렬을 할 때 당연하다는 듯이 Flex 를 사용해서 구현하고는 합니다. 웹 페이지는 기본적으로 수직으로 구성되어 있으며 수직으로 스크롤하며 화면을 읽게 됩니다. HTML Elements들은 대부분 <code class=\"language-text\">display: block</code> 속성을 가지고 있기 때문에 수직으로 Element들을 수직으로 쌓는 것은 쉽게 가능하지만 수평으로 쌓는 것은 다릅니다.</p>\n<p>Flex를 알기 전에는 주로 요소에 <code class=\"language-text\">float: left</code> 속성을 주어 수평정렬을 구성하였는데요 Flex를 사용하면 더 쉽게 레이아웃을 구성할 수 있으며 반응형 디자인에도 적합하다고 생각합니다.</p>\n<p>모든 속성을 다 배우기보다는 활용하기 좋은 속성을 위주로 진행해보겠습니다.</p>\n<p>Flex는 Flexible Box, Flex Box 라고도 불리우며 두 가지 요소로 분리됩니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Flex Container(플렉스 컨테이너)</li>\n<li>Flex Items(플렉스 아이템)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>이름만들어도 어느정도 유추가능한데요, Flex Container라는 부모요소가 Flex의 영향을 받으며, 설정된 속성에 따라서 각각의 Flex Items가 배치되게 됩니다.</p>\n<p>그리고 이런 Flex Container와 Flex Items에 적용될 수 있는 속성도 각각 존재합니다.</p>\n<h2>Flex Container</h2>\n<p>Flex Container의 속성은 다음과 같습니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>display</li>\n<li>flex-direction</li>\n<li>flex-wrap</li>\n<li>flex-flow</li>\n<li>justify-content</li>\n<li>align-content</li>\n<li>align-items</li>\n<li>gap</li>\n</ul>\n<p>간단한 Flex 레이아웃을 만들어 보겠습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\">// index.html\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>container<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>  \n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>item<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>item1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>  \n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>item<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>item2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>  \n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>item<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>item3<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>  \n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* index.css */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.container</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  \n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> flex<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  // <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> inline-flex<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>위와 같은 레이아웃은 화면에 다음과 같이 출력됩니다.!\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5e286072abdad754c8078124dec032a8/fe147/flex.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 19.270833333333332%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/5e286072abdad754c8078124dec032a8/a59e9/flex.webp 192w,\n/static/5e286072abdad754c8078124dec032a8/0ca9f/flex.webp 384w,\n/static/5e286072abdad754c8078124dec032a8/dc9b9/flex.webp 768w,\n/static/5e286072abdad754c8078124dec032a8/e2c2f/flex.webp 1152w,\n/static/5e286072abdad754c8078124dec032a8/f3efb/flex.webp 1536w,\n/static/5e286072abdad754c8078124dec032a8/50ff9/flex.webp 1604w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/5e286072abdad754c8078124dec032a8/3b721/flex.png 192w,\n/static/5e286072abdad754c8078124dec032a8/66595/flex.png 384w,\n/static/5e286072abdad754c8078124dec032a8/fe486/flex.png 768w,\n/static/5e286072abdad754c8078124dec032a8/d2d74/flex.png 1152w,\n/static/5e286072abdad754c8078124dec032a8/e8464/flex.png 1536w,\n/static/5e286072abdad754c8078124dec032a8/fe147/flex.png 1604w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/5e286072abdad754c8078124dec032a8/fe486/flex.png\"\n            alt=\"flex\"\n            title=\"flex\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Flex Items들이 수평으로 배치되며 item의 width만큼 자리를 차지하고 height값을 직접 지정해주지 않으면 Flex Container의 height만큼 늘어나게 됩니다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">display: inline-flex</code>의 경우에는 다음과 같이 출력됩니다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a8c8b9181040f9de0edfab75d8a4e1b0/fe147/inline-flex.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 18.75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/a8c8b9181040f9de0edfab75d8a4e1b0/a59e9/inline-flex.webp 192w,\n/static/a8c8b9181040f9de0edfab75d8a4e1b0/0ca9f/inline-flex.webp 384w,\n/static/a8c8b9181040f9de0edfab75d8a4e1b0/dc9b9/inline-flex.webp 768w,\n/static/a8c8b9181040f9de0edfab75d8a4e1b0/e2c2f/inline-flex.webp 1152w,\n/static/a8c8b9181040f9de0edfab75d8a4e1b0/f3efb/inline-flex.webp 1536w,\n/static/a8c8b9181040f9de0edfab75d8a4e1b0/50ff9/inline-flex.webp 1604w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/a8c8b9181040f9de0edfab75d8a4e1b0/3b721/inline-flex.png 192w,\n/static/a8c8b9181040f9de0edfab75d8a4e1b0/66595/inline-flex.png 384w,\n/static/a8c8b9181040f9de0edfab75d8a4e1b0/fe486/inline-flex.png 768w,\n/static/a8c8b9181040f9de0edfab75d8a4e1b0/d2d74/inline-flex.png 1152w,\n/static/a8c8b9181040f9de0edfab75d8a4e1b0/e8464/inline-flex.png 1536w,\n/static/a8c8b9181040f9de0edfab75d8a4e1b0/fe147/inline-flex.png 1604w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/a8c8b9181040f9de0edfab75d8a4e1b0/fe486/inline-flex.png\"\n            alt=\"inline flex\"\n            title=\"inline flex\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">display: flex</code>는 block 요소와 같이 수직으로 쌓이며 <code class=\"language-text\">display: inline-flex</code>는 inline 요소와 같이 수평적으로 쌓이는 특성을 가지게 됩니다. block과 inline-block을 생각하시면 됩니다.\n여기서 얘기하는 수직, 수평으로 쌓이는 것은 Flex Items를 말하는 것이 아닌 Flex Container를 말하는 것임을 주의해주세요.</p>\n<p>먼저 Flex Container의 속성들을 알아보겠습니다.</p>\n<h3>flex-direction</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">flex-direction</code> 속성으로 flex items를 어느 방향으로 배치 할 것인지(메인축) 설정할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>메인축(Main Axis): item들이 배치된 방향의 축</p>\n<p>교차축(Cross Axis): 메인축과 수직으로 교차하는 축</p>\n</blockquote>\n<br />\n위에서 만들어 본 레이아웃을 예시로 들어보겠습니다.\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/72f919b7889d3223292e8e22baf41914/1855e/axis.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 19.791666666666668%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/72f919b7889d3223292e8e22baf41914/a59e9/axis.webp 192w,\n/static/72f919b7889d3223292e8e22baf41914/0ca9f/axis.webp 384w,\n/static/72f919b7889d3223292e8e22baf41914/dc9b9/axis.webp 768w,\n/static/72f919b7889d3223292e8e22baf41914/e2c2f/axis.webp 1152w,\n/static/72f919b7889d3223292e8e22baf41914/f3efb/axis.webp 1536w,\n/static/72f919b7889d3223292e8e22baf41914/38bbb/axis.webp 1546w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/72f919b7889d3223292e8e22baf41914/3b721/axis.png 192w,\n/static/72f919b7889d3223292e8e22baf41914/66595/axis.png 384w,\n/static/72f919b7889d3223292e8e22baf41914/fe486/axis.png 768w,\n/static/72f919b7889d3223292e8e22baf41914/d2d74/axis.png 1152w,\n/static/72f919b7889d3223292e8e22baf41914/e8464/axis.png 1536w,\n/static/72f919b7889d3223292e8e22baf41914/1855e/axis.png 1546w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/72f919b7889d3223292e8e22baf41914/fe486/axis.png\"\n            alt=\"axis\"\n            title=\"axis\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br />\n<p>메인축(Main Axis)와 교차축(Cross Axis)를 이해하고있으면 flex를 이해하기 더 쉽습니다!</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">flex-direction</code> 속성을 사용해서 item들이 배치되는 방향 (메인축)을 정해줄 수 있습니다.</p>\n<br />\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/971c5535939048556d0abd8c1af82fa6/22593/flex-direction.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 115.625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/971c5535939048556d0abd8c1af82fa6/a59e9/flex-direction.webp 192w,\n/static/971c5535939048556d0abd8c1af82fa6/0ca9f/flex-direction.webp 384w,\n/static/971c5535939048556d0abd8c1af82fa6/dc9b9/flex-direction.webp 768w,\n/static/971c5535939048556d0abd8c1af82fa6/e6a9b/flex-direction.webp 1106w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/971c5535939048556d0abd8c1af82fa6/3b721/flex-direction.png 192w,\n/static/971c5535939048556d0abd8c1af82fa6/66595/flex-direction.png 384w,\n/static/971c5535939048556d0abd8c1af82fa6/fe486/flex-direction.png 768w,\n/static/971c5535939048556d0abd8c1af82fa6/22593/flex-direction.png 1106w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/971c5535939048556d0abd8c1af82fa6/fe486/flex-direction.png\"\n            alt=\"flex direction\"\n            title=\"flex direction\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>flex-wrap</h3>\n<p>Flex에서는 기본적으로 items들의 크기가 container의 요소보다 커지더라도 한 줄에서만 (메인축으로) 표시가 되고 줄 바꿈되지가 않습니다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">flex-wrap</code>은 items의 여러 줄 묶음(줄 바꿈)을 설정할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ed450822ba9a68770f363b6b4fcb104d/3553b/flex-wrap.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.8125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/ed450822ba9a68770f363b6b4fcb104d/a59e9/flex-wrap.webp 192w,\n/static/ed450822ba9a68770f363b6b4fcb104d/0ca9f/flex-wrap.webp 384w,\n/static/ed450822ba9a68770f363b6b4fcb104d/dc9b9/flex-wrap.webp 768w,\n/static/ed450822ba9a68770f363b6b4fcb104d/e2c2f/flex-wrap.webp 1152w,\n/static/ed450822ba9a68770f363b6b4fcb104d/f3efb/flex-wrap.webp 1536w,\n/static/ed450822ba9a68770f363b6b4fcb104d/904ef/flex-wrap.webp 1732w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/ed450822ba9a68770f363b6b4fcb104d/3b721/flex-wrap.png 192w,\n/static/ed450822ba9a68770f363b6b4fcb104d/66595/flex-wrap.png 384w,\n/static/ed450822ba9a68770f363b6b4fcb104d/fe486/flex-wrap.png 768w,\n/static/ed450822ba9a68770f363b6b4fcb104d/d2d74/flex-wrap.png 1152w,\n/static/ed450822ba9a68770f363b6b4fcb104d/e8464/flex-wrap.png 1536w,\n/static/ed450822ba9a68770f363b6b4fcb104d/3553b/flex-wrap.png 1732w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/ed450822ba9a68770f363b6b4fcb104d/fe486/flex-wrap.png\"\n            alt=\"flex wrap\"\n            title=\"flex wrap\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>지금까지 <code class=\"language-text\">flex-direction</code> 속성과 <code class=\"language-text\">flex-wrap</code>을 알아보았는데요, 이 속성을 한 속성에서 설정해줄 수도 있습니다.</p>\n<h3>flex-flow</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">/* flex-flow: [flex-direction] [flex-wrap] */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">flex-flow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> column wrap<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>justify-content</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">justify-content</code> 속성을 사용하면 메인 축(main-axis)의 정렬 방법을 설정할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/dab0ae601aa0fc28f7e06a20becc5561/b59ab/justify-content.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 143.22916666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/dab0ae601aa0fc28f7e06a20becc5561/a59e9/justify-content.webp 192w,\n/static/dab0ae601aa0fc28f7e06a20becc5561/0ca9f/justify-content.webp 384w,\n/static/dab0ae601aa0fc28f7e06a20becc5561/dc9b9/justify-content.webp 768w,\n/static/dab0ae601aa0fc28f7e06a20becc5561/426c3/justify-content.webp 922w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/dab0ae601aa0fc28f7e06a20becc5561/3b721/justify-content.png 192w,\n/static/dab0ae601aa0fc28f7e06a20becc5561/66595/justify-content.png 384w,\n/static/dab0ae601aa0fc28f7e06a20becc5561/fe486/justify-content.png 768w,\n/static/dab0ae601aa0fc28f7e06a20becc5561/b59ab/justify-content.png 922w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/dab0ae601aa0fc28f7e06a20becc5561/fe486/justify-content.png\"\n            alt=\"justify content\"\n            title=\"justify content\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">space-around</code>와 <code class=\"language-text\">space-between</code>의 차이점이 미묘해 보일 수 있는데요</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">space-between</code>은 첫번째 item을 시작점에, 마지막 item을 끝점에 두고 나머지 여백을 골고루 지정해줍니다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">space-around</code>는 item들의 사이의 여백을 골고루 지정해줍니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<br />\n<br />\n<h3>align-content</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">align-content</code> 속성을 사용하면 교차 축(cross-axis)의 정렬 방법을 설정할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ce17a7a17dc6f2fd6c0c2e57606ff8fa/e9d40/align-content.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 137.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/ce17a7a17dc6f2fd6c0c2e57606ff8fa/a59e9/align-content.webp 192w,\n/static/ce17a7a17dc6f2fd6c0c2e57606ff8fa/0ca9f/align-content.webp 384w,\n/static/ce17a7a17dc6f2fd6c0c2e57606ff8fa/dc9b9/align-content.webp 768w,\n/static/ce17a7a17dc6f2fd6c0c2e57606ff8fa/be29d/align-content.webp 1014w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/ce17a7a17dc6f2fd6c0c2e57606ff8fa/3b721/align-content.png 192w,\n/static/ce17a7a17dc6f2fd6c0c2e57606ff8fa/66595/align-content.png 384w,\n/static/ce17a7a17dc6f2fd6c0c2e57606ff8fa/fe486/align-content.png 768w,\n/static/ce17a7a17dc6f2fd6c0c2e57606ff8fa/e9d40/align-content.png 1014w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/ce17a7a17dc6f2fd6c0c2e57606ff8fa/fe486/align-content.png\"\n            alt=\"align content\"\n            title=\"align content\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>align-items</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">align-items</code> 속성을 사용하면 교차 축(cross-axis)에서 items의 정렬 방법을 설정할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7f81e2c8f838d8fd4302dd8523834b64/02a0d/align-items.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 89.58333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/7f81e2c8f838d8fd4302dd8523834b64/a59e9/align-items.webp 192w,\n/static/7f81e2c8f838d8fd4302dd8523834b64/0ca9f/align-items.webp 384w,\n/static/7f81e2c8f838d8fd4302dd8523834b64/dc9b9/align-items.webp 768w,\n/static/7f81e2c8f838d8fd4302dd8523834b64/e2c2f/align-items.webp 1152w,\n/static/7f81e2c8f838d8fd4302dd8523834b64/d1d4a/align-items.webp 1478w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/7f81e2c8f838d8fd4302dd8523834b64/3b721/align-items.png 192w,\n/static/7f81e2c8f838d8fd4302dd8523834b64/66595/align-items.png 384w,\n/static/7f81e2c8f838d8fd4302dd8523834b64/fe486/align-items.png 768w,\n/static/7f81e2c8f838d8fd4302dd8523834b64/d2d74/align-items.png 1152w,\n/static/7f81e2c8f838d8fd4302dd8523834b64/02a0d/align-items.png 1478w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/7f81e2c8f838d8fd4302dd8523834b64/fe486/align-items.png\"\n            alt=\"align items\"\n            title=\"align items\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>gap</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">gap</code> 속성을 사용하면 items들의 사이사이 간격들을 설정할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<h2>Flex Items</h2>\n<p>Flex Items의 속성은 다음과 같습니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>order</li>\n<li>flex-grow</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>order</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">order</code> 속성을 사용하면 item의 순서를 설정할 수 있습니다. order의 값으로 items의 정렬 순서가 결정됩니다. order의 기본값은 0입니다.</p>\n<p>아이템의 순서를 바꾸고 싶을 때 사용할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e40b66512d4fa507c0d75d50d70e3d6b/7b3ec/order.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 41.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/e40b66512d4fa507c0d75d50d70e3d6b/a59e9/order.webp 192w,\n/static/e40b66512d4fa507c0d75d50d70e3d6b/0ca9f/order.webp 384w,\n/static/e40b66512d4fa507c0d75d50d70e3d6b/dc9b9/order.webp 768w,\n/static/e40b66512d4fa507c0d75d50d70e3d6b/e2c2f/order.webp 1152w,\n/static/e40b66512d4fa507c0d75d50d70e3d6b/98c65/order.webp 1284w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/e40b66512d4fa507c0d75d50d70e3d6b/3b721/order.png 192w,\n/static/e40b66512d4fa507c0d75d50d70e3d6b/66595/order.png 384w,\n/static/e40b66512d4fa507c0d75d50d70e3d6b/fe486/order.png 768w,\n/static/e40b66512d4fa507c0d75d50d70e3d6b/d2d74/order.png 1152w,\n/static/e40b66512d4fa507c0d75d50d70e3d6b/7b3ec/order.png 1284w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/e40b66512d4fa507c0d75d50d70e3d6b/fe486/order.png\"\n            alt=\"order\"\n            title=\"order\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>flex-grow</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">flex-grow</code> 속성을 사용하면 item들의 증가 너비 비율을 설정할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bcc9bea77e9ad24e9f5433a39261041c/6d3ba/flex-grow.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.3125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/bcc9bea77e9ad24e9f5433a39261041c/a59e9/flex-grow.webp 192w,\n/static/bcc9bea77e9ad24e9f5433a39261041c/0ca9f/flex-grow.webp 384w,\n/static/bcc9bea77e9ad24e9f5433a39261041c/dc9b9/flex-grow.webp 768w,\n/static/bcc9bea77e9ad24e9f5433a39261041c/e2c2f/flex-grow.webp 1152w,\n/static/bcc9bea77e9ad24e9f5433a39261041c/f3efb/flex-grow.webp 1536w,\n/static/bcc9bea77e9ad24e9f5433a39261041c/6ecb5/flex-grow.webp 1774w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/bcc9bea77e9ad24e9f5433a39261041c/3b721/flex-grow.png 192w,\n/static/bcc9bea77e9ad24e9f5433a39261041c/66595/flex-grow.png 384w,\n/static/bcc9bea77e9ad24e9f5433a39261041c/fe486/flex-grow.png 768w,\n/static/bcc9bea77e9ad24e9f5433a39261041c/d2d74/flex-grow.png 1152w,\n/static/bcc9bea77e9ad24e9f5433a39261041c/e8464/flex-grow.png 1536w,\n/static/bcc9bea77e9ad24e9f5433a39261041c/6d3ba/flex-grow.png 1774w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/bcc9bea77e9ad24e9f5433a39261041c/fe486/flex-grow.png\"\n            alt=\"flex grow\"\n            title=\"flex grow\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br />\n<p>이렇게 Flex와 Flex의 여러 속성들을 알아보았는데요. 이 글에서 이야기하지 않은 속성들도 많이 있으니 더 궁금하시다면 아래 참고 자료를 찾아보시면 좋을것 같습니다.\n<br /></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.heropy.dev/p/Ha29GI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.heropy.dev/p/Ha29GI</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://studiomeal.com/archives/197\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://studiomeal.com/archives/197</a></p>\n</blockquote>","frontmatter":{"title":"CSS Flex","summary":"Flex 해보렸지 모얌","date":"2024-07-13","categories":["CSS"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/2df6bd11efdc8de0ac54d805ca1ba1ab/97099/til.jpg","srcSet":"/static/2df6bd11efdc8de0ac54d805ca1ba1ab/d75cc/til.jpg 557w,\n/static/2df6bd11efdc8de0ac54d805ca1ba1ab/a3617/til.jpg 1113w,\n/static/2df6bd11efdc8de0ac54d805ca1ba1ab/97099/til.jpg 2226w","sizes":"(min-width: 2226px) 2226px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/2df6bd11efdc8de0ac54d805ca1ba1ab/9e13a/til.webp 557w,\n/static/2df6bd11efdc8de0ac54d805ca1ba1ab/f9e0a/til.webp 1113w,\n/static/2df6bd11efdc8de0ac54d805ca1ba1ab/b09bd/til.webp 2226w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 2226px) 2226px, 100vw"}]},"width":2226,"height":1322}},"publicURL":"/static/2df6bd11efdc8de0ac54d805ca1ba1ab/til.jpg"}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Flex/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}